        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/mental-health-care-plan-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Mental Health Care Plan Sydney: how to get one and what it covers</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Step-by-step guide to getting a Mental Health Treatment Plan (MHTP) from your GP: what to say at the appointment, how many sessions Medicare covers (10 per year), renewals, and how to use it for telehealth psychology.</p>
          <a href="/guides/mental-health-care-plan-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the MHTP guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/social-anxiety-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Social anxiety: telehealth psychology in Sydney</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What social anxiety disorder is, how CBT and exposure work for it (including via telehealth), why telehealth suits many people with social anxiety, what the research shows, and what to look for in a psychologist.</p>
          <a href="/guides/social-anxiety-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the social anxiety guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/how-to-choose-anxiety-psychologist-telehealth/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">How to choose a telehealth psychologist for anxiety</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What to look for in a psychologist: AHPRA registration, registered vs clinical explained plainly, therapy approaches (CBT, ACT, EMDR) in plain English, questions to ask before booking, and how to know if telehealth suits your situation.</p>
