          <a href="/guides/ocd-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the OCD guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/generalised-anxiety-disorder-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Generalised anxiety disorder (GAD): telehealth psychology in Sydney</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What GAD is and how it differs from everyday worry, how CBT (including intolerance of uncertainty work) and ACT treat it, why telehealth suits GAD well, and what to look for in a psychologist.</p>
          <a href="/guides/generalised-anxiety-disorder-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the GAD guide &rarr;</a>
