          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">All the public data on how many Australians use Medicare psychology, anxiety disorder prevalence by type (3.3 million people, 17% of adults), workforce supply by state, expenditure, and access gaps. Real figures from AIHW, ABS, and the MBS.</p>
