          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What PTSD and complex PTSD are, evidence-based treatments (Prolonged Exposure, CPT, EMDR), why telehealth is appropriate for trauma work, clinical safety considerations, and how to identify a PTSD-specialist psychologist. Medicare rebates apply.</p>
          <a href="/guides/ptsd-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the PTSD guide &rarr;</a>
