          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">How anxiety and depression co-occur, why they are treated together rather than sequentially, how CBT and ACT address both, and what to look for in a psychologist when both are present. Medicare costs explained.</p>
          <a href="/guides/anxiety-depression-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the anxiety + depression guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.15rem;"><a href="/guides/evening-weekend-psychologist-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Evening and weekend telehealth psychologist in Sydney</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">How to find a psychologist with late afternoon, early morning, or Saturday appointments in Sydney. Realistic guide to flexible hours, what telehealth enables, and how Medicare rebates apply regardless of session time.</p>
          <a href="/guides/evening-weekend-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the evening and weekend guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
