          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">What agoraphobia is and how it differs from general panic, why telehealth is often the most practical first step, how CBT and graduated exposure work, and what to look for in a psychologist. Medicare rebates apply.</p>
          <a href="/guides/agoraphobia-telehealth-psychologist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the agoraphobia guide &rarr;</a>
        </div>

